name: hdc_streaming_2k
version: "1.0.0"
language: zig
module: hdc_streaming_2k

description: |
  HDC Streaming 2K — Level 10A.9: 2000+ Token Coherent Long-Form Generation.
  Extends streaming to novel-length output with multi-level coherence tracking,
  hierarchical topic memory, and adaptive generation control.

  === 2000+ TOKEN ARCHITECTURE ===
  Generating 2000+ tokens requires maintaining coherence far beyond the
  128-token context window. Three hierarchical memory levels:

  Level 1: CONTEXT WINDOW (128 tokens)
    Standard sliding window with importance-based eviction.
    Captures local character/word patterns.
    Updated every token.

  Level 2: PARAGRAPH MEMORY (last 5 paragraphs)
    topic_hv per paragraph, stored as fixed set of 5 summary HVs.
    When new paragraph starts, oldest paragraph summary evicted.
    Injected into attention as 5 synthetic KV-cache entries.
    Captures paragraph-level themes and transitions.
    Updated at paragraph boundaries.

  Level 3: DOCUMENT MEMORY (entire generation)
    Global topic_hv = bundleN(all generated token HVs) via running bundle2.
    Single HV summarizing everything generated so far.
    Injected as 1 synthetic KV-cache entry (always present).
    Captures overall document topic and style.
    Updated every token (O(1) via incremental bundle2).

  Total synthetic entries: 5 (paragraph) + 1 (document) = 6.
  Effective context: 128 + 6 = 134 positions in KV-cache.
  Additional latency per token: 6 * (bind + cosine) = 6 * (2129+190) = 13,914 ns ≈ 14 us.
  Total per-token cost: ~170 us + 14 us = 184 us.

  === GENERATION CONTROL ===

  1. TEMPERATURE SCHEDULING
    Tokens 1-50: T=0.7 (focused start, establish topic)
    Tokens 51-500: T=0.9 (explore, develop ideas)
    Tokens 501-1500: T=0.85 (balanced, maintain coherence)
    Tokens 1501-2000: T=0.7 (focused ending, wrap up)
    Custom: user-defined schedule function

  2. REPETITION CONTROL
    Short-range: penalize chars repeated in last 20 tokens (penalty=1.2)
    Medium-range: penalize 3-grams repeated in last 200 tokens (penalty=1.5)
    Long-range: penalize sentences repeated in last 1000 tokens (penalty=2.0)
    Detection: maintain hash set of 3-grams and sentence hashes.

  3. STRUCTURAL PROMPTS
    At paragraph boundary (detected by punctuation + newline pattern):
      Inject newline token, reduce temperature for 5 tokens.
    Every 500 tokens without paragraph break:
      Force paragraph break (inject \n\n + reduce temperature).
    At 1800 tokens: begin conclusion mode (lower temperature, bias toward
      sentence-ending punctuation).

  4. CONFIDENCE MONITORING
    Track rolling average confidence over last 50 tokens.
    If avg_confidence < 0.05 for 10 consecutive tokens:
      Model is generating noise → activate recovery:
        1. Reset temperature to 0.5
        2. Increase top_k to 10
        3. Inject document summary into attention with weight 2x
        4. Continue for 20 tokens, then restore settings
    If avg_confidence < 0.02: stop generation (quality too low).

  === PERFORMANCE (2000 tokens, D=256, H=3, ctx=128) ===
  Phase 1 (tokens 1-8): full forward, 389 us
  Phase 2 (tokens 9-128): growing cache, avg 90 us
  Phase 3 (tokens 129-2000): sliding window, 184 us (with memory injection)

  Breakdown:
    8 * 389 us     =     3.1 ms  (Phase 1)
    120 * 90 us    =    10.8 ms  (Phase 2)
    1872 * 184 us  =   344.4 ms  (Phase 3)
    TOTAL          =   358.3 ms
    Average: 179 us/token = ~5,590 tokens/sec

  === MULTILINGUAL 2K STREAMING ===
  Each language gets independent generation session.
  Codebook shared across languages (all chars coexist).
  Language detection on seed text determines output metrics grouping.
  Cross-lingual generation possible if seed mixes languages.

  Test matrix:
    7 languages x 2000 tokens = 14,000 total tokens generated
    Expected total time: 7 * 358 ms = 2.5 seconds
    Quality targets per language:
      unique_ratio > 0.12 (12%+ unique chars over 2000 tokens)
      repetition_rate < 0.08 (8% consecutive duplicates acceptable)
      paragraphs >= 5 (structured long-form)
      avg_confidence > 0.08

  Trinity Identity: phi^2 + 1/phi^2 = 3
  Sacred Formula: V = n * 3^k * pi^m * phi^p * e^q

types:
  MemoryLevel:
    enum:
      - context_window
      - paragraph_memory
      - document_memory

  ParagraphSummary:
    fields:
      paragraph_index: usize
      start_token: usize
      end_token: usize
      summary_hv: List<i8>
      sentence_count: usize
      dominant_chars: List<String>

  DocumentMemory:
    fields:
      global_topic_hv: List<i8>
      total_tokens_accumulated: usize
      paragraph_summaries: List<ParagraphSummary>
      max_paragraph_summaries: usize

  TemperatureSchedule:
    fields:
      phases: List<Float>
      phase_boundaries: List<usize>
      current_temperature: Float
      conclusion_start: usize

  RepetitionTracker:
    fields:
      recent_tokens: List<String>
      short_window: usize
      trigram_hashes: List<u64>
      sentence_hashes: List<u64>
      short_penalty: Float
      medium_penalty: Float
      long_penalty: Float

  ConfidenceTracker:
    fields:
      rolling_window: List<Float>
      window_size: usize
      avg_confidence: Float
      low_confidence_streak: usize
      recovery_active: Bool
      recovery_tokens_remaining: usize

  GenerationPhase:
    enum:
      - establishing
      - developing
      - maintaining
      - concluding

  Stream2KSession:
    fields:
      session_id: String
      seed_text: String
      language: String
      generated_text: String
      total_tokens: usize
      unique_tokens: usize
      paragraph_count: usize
      avg_confidence: Float
      min_confidence: Float
      total_time_ms: Float
      tokens_per_second: Float
      repetition_rate: Float
      phase: GenerationPhase
      memory_injections: usize
      recoveries_triggered: usize

  Stream2KReport:
    fields:
      sessions: List<Stream2KSession>
      total_tokens_generated: usize
      avg_throughput: Float
      avg_coherence: Float
      quality_targets_met: Bool

  HDCStreaming2K:
    fields:
      allocator: Allocator
      config: LongStreamConfig
      runtime: HDCEndToEndRuntime
      document_memory: DocumentMemory
      temp_schedule: TemperatureSchedule
      repetition: RepetitionTracker
      confidence: ConfidenceTracker

behaviors:
  - name: initStreaming2K
    given: LongStreamConfig with max_tokens >= 2000 and trained runtime
    when: Initialize 3-level memory, temperature schedule, repetition tracker
    then: 2K streaming engine ready for long-form generation

  - name: generate2K
    given: Seed text and generation config
    when: Full pipeline: seed → memory init → loop(forward → decode → memory → control → yield)
    then: Returns Stream2KSession with 2000+ tokens and quality metrics

  - name: initDocumentMemory
    given: Dimension D and max_paragraph_summaries (5)
    when: Zero global_topic_hv, empty paragraph list
    then: Document memory ready for accumulation

  - name: updateDocumentMemory
    given: New generated token HV
    when: global_topic_hv = vsa.bundle2(global_topic_hv, token_hv)
    then: Document memory reflects all generated content (O(1) update)

  - name: addParagraphSummary
    given: Completed paragraph tokens
    when: Compute paragraph_hv = bundleN(paragraph_token_hvs), evict oldest if > 5
    then: Paragraph memory updated with latest summary

  - name: injectMemoryIntoAttention
    given: KV-cache and memory HVs (5 paragraph + 1 document)
    when: Add 6 synthetic (K, V) entries at positions after real context
    then: Attention can attend to paragraph and document summaries

  - name: computeTemperature
    given: Current token position and schedule
    when: Look up phase from boundaries, return scheduled temperature
    then: Temperature appropriate for generation phase

  - name: activateConclusionMode
    given: Token position >= conclusion_start (1800)
    when: Lower temperature, bias toward punctuation and uppercase
    then: Generation naturally wraps toward ending

  - name: trackRepetition
    given: New token and existing repetition tracker
    when: Update 3-gram hashes, sentence hashes, check penalties
    then: Repetition penalties computed for current decoding step

  - name: penalizeRepetition
    given: Candidate similarities and repetition tracker
    when: Apply short/medium/long-range penalties to matching candidates
    then: Repeated tokens penalized at appropriate severity

  - name: trackConfidence
    given: Current token confidence score
    when: Update rolling window, compute average, check streak
    then: Confidence tracker updated, recovery triggered if needed

  - name: activateRecovery
    given: Low confidence streak >= 10 tokens
    when: Reset T=0.5, increase top_k=10, inject document summary with 2x weight
    then: Recovery mode active for 20 tokens

  - name: deactivateRecovery
    given: Recovery tokens expired or confidence restored
    when: Restore original temperature, top_k, memory weights
    then: Normal generation resumed

  - name: forceStructure
    given: 500 tokens without paragraph break
    when: Inject newline tokens, reduce temperature for 5 tokens
    then: Forced paragraph break for readability

  - name: generate2KMultilingual
    given: 7 seed texts in different languages, 2000 tokens each
    when: Run generate2K for each seed, collect per-language metrics
    then: Returns Stream2KReport with 14,000+ total tokens

  - name: checkQualityTargets
    given: Completed Stream2KSession
    when: Verify unique_ratio, repetition_rate, paragraphs, confidence thresholds
    then: Returns quality assessment with per-criterion pass/fail

  - name: generateReport
    given: Stream2KReport
    when: Format sessions, quality targets, cross-language comparison
    then: Returns markdown report for documentation
